{{Infobox person | name = Deirdre Bolton | image = | caption = Deirdre Bolton | birthname = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1971|09|21}}<ref>https://marriedbiography.com/deirdre-bolton-biography/</ref> | birth_place = [[Newtown Township, Bucks County, Pennsylvania|Newtown, PA]], U.S. | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | age = | education = | occupation = [[journalist]], [[news anchor]] | alma_mater = [[University of Iowa]], [[New York University]] | status = | title = | relatives = | ethnicity = | religion = | salary = | networth = | credits = | agent = | URL = }}
'''Deirdre Bolton''' (born September 21, 1971)<ref>https://marriedbiography.com/deirdre-bolton-biography/</ref> is an American [[News presenter|television anchor]] and host of ''Risk & Reward'' on [[Fox Business Network]] <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxbusiness.com/person/b/deirdre-bolton|title=Deirdre Bolton|publisher=[[Fox Business]]|accessdate=March 29, 2018}}</ref> Bolton lives in [[New York (state)|New York]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.press-citizen.com/story/news/education/university-of-iowa/2014/04/30/university-of-iowa-fox-business-network-deidre-bolton/8521835/|title=UI Alumna to Host Show on Fox Business Network|last=Agnew|first=Sara|date=30 April 2014|work=Iowa City Press-Citizen|access-date=26 June 2016|via=}}</ref>
==Biography== Deirdre Bolton graduated from the [[University of Iowa]] with a degree in English and French literature in 1993. She graduated Council Rock High School in Bucks County Pennsylvania in 1989.<ref name=":0" /> She holds a master's degree from [[New York University]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=bwh&AN=bizwire.c53204453&site=ehost-live|title=Fox Business Network Signs Bloomberg’s Deirdre Bolton|last=|first=|date=5 February 2014|work=Business Wire|subscription=yes|access-date=26 June 2016|via=EBSCO}}</ref>
Bolton formerly anchored Bloomberg Television's ''Money Moves'', a show about alternative investments. She started at Bloomberg in 2009.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/fox-business-to-launch-new-deirdre-bolton-program-march-31-1201137955/|title=Fox Business To Launch New Deirdre Bolton Program March 31|last=Steinberg|first=Brian|date=2014|work=Variety|access-date=26 June 2016|via=}}</ref> On January 31, 2014 she left Bloomberg for Fox Business News to host a new business show ''Risk & Reward''.<ref>La Roche, Julia (January 31, 2014) [http://www.businessinsider.com/deirdre-bolton-is-leaving-bloomberg-2014-1 EXCLUSIVE: Star Anchor Deirdre Bolton Is Leaving Bloomberg TV For Fox Business Network]. businessinsider.com</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|date=21 March 2014|title=Fox Business Network to Roll out Risk and Reward Program with Deirdre Bolton|url=https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-35824088.html|journal=Manufacturing Close-Up|doi=|pmid=|access-date=26 June 2016|subscription=yes|via=HighBeam Research}}</ref> However, Bolton was absent from the show for nearly a year due to an injury she sustained in the summer of 2016 that required a long recovery time.<ref>{{cite web|last=Ariens|first=Chris|url=http://www.adweek.com/tvnewser/deirdre-bolton-returns-to-fox-business/338031|title=Deirdre Bolton Returns to Fox Business|publisher=''[[Adweek]]''|date=August 15, 2017}}</ref>
